## Troubleshooting

### "CORS error" after setting up proxy

1. Check your proxy is running: `curl https://your-proxy.com/health`
2. Verify your origin is in the allowed list
3. Check browser console for specific error message

### "502 Bad Gateway"

1. Check the target provider is accessible
2. Verify your API key is correct
3. Check proxy server logs for errors

### Requests are slow

1. Choose a proxy location close to the AI provider
2. Cloudflare Workers are globally distributed and typically fastest
3. Consider connection pooling for self-hosted solutions

